thread.title: Sherry

author: Sherry
title: Sherry
text: I wasn't sure about selling my phone to a company on-line but a friend of mine had done it and said that it was easy... so I thought I'd give it a go. They were right I received my shipping labels within a couple of days mailed my devices right back the next day and within a week I had my payment for the agreed upon amount. I am very impressed and will continue to use Maxback in my future cell phone endeavors.
